description: Quickly look up the recipes for several popular drinks just by asking fancy bartender. If you're making for friends, just ask how to make several of them. It's as simple as that!
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask fancy bartender what I need to make six long islands
Ask fancy bartender how to make a blue hawaiian
Ask fancy bartender what is in a white russian
name: Fancy Bartender
shortDescription: Want to wind down or turn up with a nice cocktail? Ask fancy bartender how to make one!
